text.tspan: Hey, Mike! It's Dave. This note is very important
so I need you to read it.
The new artifact I mentioned when we were
texting each other is actually an animatronic.
I heard that it is known for its nocturnal activity
Below are some stuff that should help you defend
Try to blind it with your flashlight. Make sure to
flash your light DIRECTLY at its face.
That animatronic might run to your
left past the window. Be quick and
try to flash it before it makes it to
If it's ever seen crawling through one of the vent shafts,
seal that respective vent shut. There's a system that
allows these vents to be shut (further discussed on nest page).
